    "description": "<strong><i>Charles是一辆以鲜血为食的火车，你需要前去消灭他。</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>驾驶皮实可靠的老式火车，环游广阔的可游玩区域。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/92b6e944694b29f4d49f017b18c9a43d.poster.avif?t=1718841444\" width=630 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/92b6e944694b29f4d49f017b18c9a43d.webm?t=1718841444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/92b6e944694b29f4d49f017b18c9a43d.mp4?t=1718841444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>蜿蜒曲折的轨道暗藏凶机，每个任务都需要精心筹划。徒步冒险或改变轨道时请小心行事，Charles也许正在暗处等着你呢。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级火车，满足探险所需。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/7739bcef9e5bf543b837fc020b7d1be4.poster.avif?t=1718841444\" width=630 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/7739bcef9e5bf543b837fc020b7d1be4.webm?t=1718841444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/7739bcef9e5bf543b837fc020b7d1be4.mp4?t=1718841444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过完成任务或四处搜刮获取废料，将火车改装成轮上致命机器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>拜访岛民，乐施善行，获取回报。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/602aa96dc94fb241f3397ab38648f5d7.poster.avif?t=1718841444\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/602aa96dc94fb241f3397ab38648f5d7.webm?t=1718841444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/602aa96dc94fb241f3397ab38648f5d7.mp4?t=1718841444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>帮助岛民，获取强力武器和摧毁Charles的关键物品。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与Charles决一死战</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/106ec32c1ae86885947e59be076d75fe.poster.avif?t=1718841444\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/106ec32c1ae86885947e59be076d75fe.webm?t=1718841444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766740/extras/106ec32c1ae86885947e59be076d75fe.mp4?t=1718841444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>完成主线任务，召唤查尔斯展开最终对决。如果你已获得足够强大的力量、武器和技能，或许就能成为可与Charles一较高下的终极对手。",
